{"name":"Tripod Mount","type":"itemattachment","img":"/systems/starwarsffg/images/mod-weapon.png","data":{"description":"[H3]Tripod Mount[h3]\n\nDesigned for use with the heaviest man-portable weapons, tripods are a common sight among heavy weapon squads. Used in static weapon emplacements to support heavy squad support weapons such as the Imperial Army's E-Web heavy repeating blaster, tripods use a number of different technologies—from self-extending hydraulics to tiny, low-output repulsorlift generators—to stabilize heavy weapons for firing. This attachment is only for use on light repeating blasters and heavy repeating blasters, as well as any portable Gunnery weapons. Setting up a tripod takes two preparation maneuvers. \n\n[P][B]Models Include:[b] BlasTech 3R Heavy Weapon Tripod Mount.<h3>Base Mods</h3><div>Cumbersome Quality - A Cumbersome weapon is large, unwieldy, awkward, or heavy. To wield a Cumbersome weapon properly, the character needs a Brawn characteristic equal to or greater than the weapon’s Cumbersome rating. For each point of Brawn the character is deficient, he must increase the difficulty of all checks made while using the weapon by one. </div>","attributes":{},"quantity":{"value":1,"type":"Number","label":"Quantity","abrev":"Qty"},"encumbrance":{"value":0,"type":"Number","label":"Encumbrance","abrev":"Encum","adjusted":0},"price":{"value":100,"type":"Number","label":"Price","adjusted":0},"rarity":{"value":3,"type":"Number","label":"Rarity","adjusted":0},"hardpoints":{"value":1,"type":"Number","label":"Hard Points","abrev":"HP","adjusted":0},"itemmodifier":[{"_id":"rIE0TFWFMw1dWQhb","name":"Cumbersome Quality","type":"itemmodifier","img":"/systems/starwarsffg/images/mod-weapon.png","data":{"description":"A Cumbersome weapon is large, unwieldy, awkward, or heavy. To wield a Cumbersome weapon properly, the character needs a Brawn characteristic equal to or greater than the weapon’s Cumbersome rating. For each point of Brawn the character is deficient, he must increase the difficulty of all checks made while using the weapon by one.","attributes":{},"itemmodifier":[],"adjusteditemmodifer":[],"type":"weapon","rank":-2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"Itz0X4muSsVNH8FV":3},"flags":{"starwarsffg":{"ffgimportid":"CUMBERSOME"}},"id":"eadfvd2r29apn87g"}],"adjusteditemmodifer":[],"itemattachment":[],"type":"weapon"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"Itz0X4muSsVNH8FV":3},"flags":{"starwarsffg":{"ffgimportid":"TRIPOD"}},"_id":"aHa4JqOlSiK2D5EF"}
{"name":"Deflective Plating","type":"itemattachment","img":"/systems/starwarsffg/images/mod-vehicle.png","data":{"description":"[H3]Deflective Plating[h3]\nHulls featuring these protective plates give a tradeoff between defense and maneuverability[P][H3]Sources:[h3][H4]Page 83 - Fully Operational[h4]<h3>Base Mods</h3><div>Increase Armor Mod - Increases Armor value by 1 Count 2</div><div>Decreases Handling Mod - Decreases Handling by 1 Count 2</div>","attributes":{},"quantity":{"value":1,"type":"Number","label":"Quantity","abrev":"Qty"},"encumbrance":{"value":0,"type":"Number","label":"Encumbrance","abrev":"Encum","adjusted":0},"price":{"value":700,"type":"Number","label":"Price","adjusted":0},"rarity":{"value":5,"type":"Number","label":"Rarity","adjusted":0},"hardpoints":{"value":4,"type":"Number","label":"Hard Points","abrev":"HP","adjusted":0},"itemmodifier":[{"_id":"FoiIrJw9E5Rj1mtN","name":"Increase Armor Mod","type":"itemmodifier","img":"/systems/starwarsffg/images/mod-vehicle.png","data":{"description":"Increases Armor value by 1","attributes":{},"itemmodifier":[],"adjusteditemmodifer":[],"type":"vehicle","rank":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"Itz0X4muSsVNH8FV":3},"flags":{"starwarsffg":{"ffgimportid":"ARMORADD"}},"id":"475bkng354n7bx1p"},{"_id":"26uEwvWhVxzeWHvY","name":"Increase Forward Defense Mod","type":"itemmodifier","img":"/systems/starwarsffg/images/mod-vehicle.png","data":{"description":"Increase Forward Defense by 1","attributes":{},"itemmodifier":[],"adjusteditemmodifer":[],"type":"vehicle","rank":1},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"Itz0X4muSsVNH8FV":3},"flags":{"starwarsffg":{"ffgimportid":"ADDDEFFORE"}},"id":"k26prrnto4j0hyed"},{"_id":"qzOIl6xENHjd36pO","name":"Increase Hull Trauma by Silhouette Mod","type":"itemmodifier","img":"/systems/starwarsffg/images/mod-vehicle.png","data":{"description":"Increase Hull Trauma by Silhouette","attributes":{},"itemmodifier":[],"adjusteditemmodifer