{"name":"Astrogation Droid Brain","type":"itemattachment","img":"/systems/starwarsffg/images/mod-vehicle.png","data":{"description":"[H3]Astrogation Droid Brain[h3]\n\nTo accompany its autopilot droid brain, Go-Corp has rolled out the CD-13z, an astrogation droid brain. Essentially an astromech installed directly into the ship's hull, the CD-13z can perform astrogation calculations on its own, but it is most useful for assisting in a pilot or navigator's own calculations. Despite their common origins, CD-13z droid brains are known to bicker with CD-12a autopilot droid brains when both are installed on the same vessel. \n\n[P][B]Models Include:[b] Go-Corp CD-13z astrogator droid brain.[P][H3]Sources:[h3][H4]Fly Casual[h4]<h3>Base Mods</h3><div>Adds a Droid Brain with Astrogation Skill 2 and Intellect 0 </div>","attributes":{},"quantity":{"value":1,"type":"Number","label":"Quantity","abrev":"Qty"},"encumbrance":{"value":0,"type":"Number","label":"Encumbrance","abrev":"Encum","adjusted":0},"price":{"value":7500,"type":"Number","label":"Price","adjusted":0},"rarity":{"value":6,"type":"Number","label":"Rarity","adjusted":0},"hardpoints":{"value":0,"type":"Number","label":"Hard Points","abrev":"HP","adjusted":0},"itemmodifier":[null],"adjusteditemmodifer":[],"itemattachment":[],"type":"vehicle"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"Itz0X4muSsVNH8FV":3},"flags":{"starwarsffg":{"ffgimportid":"ASTROBRAIN"}},"_id":"acpdXj1CSpZthnhi"}
{"name":"Fusial Thrust Engine","type":"itemattachment","img":"/systems/starwarsffg/images/mod-vehicle.png","data":{"description":"[H3]Fusial Thrust Engine[h3]\nFusial engines are common in starfighters, where high speed is often the most important factor.[P][H3]Sources:[h3][H4]Page 82 - Fully Operational[h4]<h3>Base Mods</h3><div>Increase Speed Mod - Increase Speed by 1 Count 3</div><div>Increases System Strain by Silhouette Mod - Increases System Strain by Silhouette Count 4</div><div>Increase Forward Defense Mod - Increase Forward Defense by 1 </div>","attributes":{},"quantity":{"value":1,"type":"Number","label":"Quantity","abrev":"Qty"},"encumbrance":{"value":0,"type":"Number","label":"Encumbrance","abrev":"Encum","adjusted":0},"price":{"value":2500,"type":"Number","label":"Price","adjusted":0},"rarity":{"value":4,"type":"Number","label":"Rarity","adjusted":0},"hardpoints":{"value":3,"type":"Number","label":"Hard Points","abrev":"HP","adjusted":0},"itemmodifier":[{"_id":"TfqDzg8fQd6VBG9V","name":"Increase Speed Mod","type":"itemmodifier","img":"/systems/starwarsffg/images/mod-vehicle.png","data":{"description":"Increase Speed by 1","attributes":{},"itemmodifier":[],"adjusteditemmodifer":[],"type":"vehicle","rank":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"Itz0X4muSsVNH8FV":3},"flags":{"starwarsffg":{"ffgimportid":"SPEEDADD"}},"id":"911q8bi0afffo7fz"},{"_id":"6PGA8jqBl5zIX14v","name":"Increase Aft Defense Mod","type":"itemmodifier","img":"/systems/starwarsffg/images/mod-vehicle.png","data":{"description":"Increase Aft Defense by 1","attributes":{},"itemmodifier":[],"adjusteditemmodifer":[],"type":"vehicle","rank":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"Itz0X4muSsVNH8FV":3},"flags":{"starwarsffg":{"ffgimportid":"ADDDEFAFT"}},"id":"0zguocdnh9fi8wiq"}],"adjusteditemmodifer":[],"itemattachment":[],"type":"vehicle"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"Itz0X4muSsVNH8FV":3},"flags":{"starwarsffg"